The All Progressives Grand Alliance (APGA), on Saturday, kicked off its national campaign with a flag-off event in Awka, the Anambra capital. Chukwuma Soludo, governor of Anambra and national leader of the party; Willie Obiano, former Anambra governor; Bianca, former ambassador and widow of Chukwuemeka Ojukwu, were among party stakeholders at the event. Below are pictures.        PHOTO CREDIT: Anambra Broadcasting Service-ABS, Awka